snippet.title: Line Segments - MathHelp.com - Pre Algebra Help
snippet.description: For a complete lesson on line segments, go to http://www.MathHelp.com - 1000+ online math lessons featuring a personal math teacher inside every lesson! In this lesson, students learn the definitions of a point, a line, a segment, and a ray. Students are then asked to name a given figure as a line, segment, or ray, and use the appropriate symbol. Finally, students are asked to draw lines, segments, and rays.
